data.value: ATTENTION: Before you use it, we hope you know that this program could be said to be a ILLIGAL PERIPHERAL PROGRAMS. We don't know how BattleEye will judge it. And if you exit from a ranking game, you will be SUSPENDED for a long time. So please use it CAREFULLY! have fun to persecute Caveria :) 警告：在你使用之前，我们希望你知道这个程序可以说就是个外挂，我们不知道BattleEye会怎么判定，并且在排名赛中会退出战局会遭到一段时间的禁赛惩罚。所以请谨慎的使用！愉快的迫害女鬼吧(`v´)b
